DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.195ft at 06:18\n-2.967ft at 08:18\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 A new blend of primary NW/WNW swell and secondary\, longer-period SSW swel
 l scheduled to fill in during the day\, showing most size over the afterno
